<lyrics>[V1]
.D                  Bm     A7
 Hark, the herald angels sing,
. D    G       A7       D
 glory to the new born King.
.D                   Bm     A
 Peace on earth and mercy mild,
. A7       E            A7
 God and sinners reconciled.
.D               G      A7
 Joyful all ye nations rise,
.D                 G       A7
 join the trumpets of the skies,

[C1]
.   G           Em
   With angelic hosts proclaim,
.   A7        D       A7    D
   Christ is born in Bethlehem,
.   G                Em
   Hark, the herald angels sing,
.   A7    D      A7       D
   glory to the new born King.

[V2]
. D            Bm    A
 Hoor die blye eng'lelied
.D        G     A      D
 Aan die Koningseun gebied:
. D                Bm       E
 &quot;Vrede op aarde - God die eer -
.A        E       E7       A
 Hy daal tot die sondaar neer.&quot;

[C2]
.   D             G        A
   Almal wat Hom liefhet, sing
.  D              G       A
   Om Hom lof en dank te bring!
.   G              Em
   Almal, juig met hart en stem:
.   A        D      A      D
   God word mens in Bethlehem
.  G             Em
   Hoor die blye eng'lelied
.  A        D     A      D   (E)
   Aan die Koningseun gebied.

[V3]
.D               Bm               A7
 Hail the heaven born Prince of peace,
.D        G      A         D
 hail the Son of righteousness,
.D                 Bm       E
 Light and life to all He brings,
.A7          E              A7
 risen with healing in His wings.
.D                G7    A7
 Mild He lays His glory by,
.D                G7       A7
 born that man no more may die,

[C3]
.   G                Em
   Born to raise the sons of earth,
.  A7      D         A       D
   born to give them a second birth,
.   G               Em
   Hark, the herald angels sing,
.  A7    D      A         D
   glory to the new born King.

[V4]
.D            Bm   A
 Jesus, ware Vredevors
.D        G     A        D
 kom vir Hom 'n volk verlos
.D              Bm   E
 Wêreldwyd, in elke land
.A      E        E7     A
 kom bevryding deur sy hand.

[P1]
.  D               G     A
   In ons nood het Hy gedaal,
.  D             G      A
   vir ons lewe duur betaal.
.  G                Em
   Vrygemaak, deur Hom gevind,
.  A      D       A      D
   is ek ook nou koningskind!
.  G             Em
   Almal deur sy koms verlos,
.  A        D         A    D  (E)
   dank en loof die Vredevors!
.      
       </lyrics>
